short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extenship application and tools for launcher extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It is a chrome extension developed for Extenship software and tools that enable you to sell without stock on Amazon.

With this application;
-You can do comparative product research between different markets of Amazon.
-You can add and edit the products you browse and review on Amazon to Clipboard.
-You can automate or manually speed up order processes during procurement.
